# Overview
This mod adds a filter curio, which can control the automatically items picking. Shift+right click to open the configuration GUI.
# Usage
Mark items in GUI, and support blacklist and whitelist modes;

Blacklist mode does not automatically pick up marked items, while whitelist mode only picks up marked items;

Initially, at most 3 marks are added, and the maximum mark capacity can be expanded by using iron ingots (6), gold ingots (9), diamonds (18) or netherite ingots (27) on the craft table.
